                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-109-off561 t18280110-109-cd562"></join>, 1 pair of trousers, value 5s.; 2 razors, value 2s.; 2 cravats, value 1s., and 1 waistcoat, value 1s.
